name: MyFavouriteCricketPlayer
0:
”Alexa, Open my cricket players”
”Alexa, Open my cricket players and tell me about Virat Kohli”
”Tell me about Virat Kohli”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my cricket players
des: The skill has few facts about 5 Indian cricket players. A user can ask Alexa to tell about those and in response will get few facts about those players. The name of the players are Sachin Tendulkar, Sourav Ganguly, Virender Sehwag, Virat Kohli and M S Dhoni. No personal information and account linking is required to enable this skill. A user can directly go to the skill store and enable it. There is no In Skill Purchase feature also.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
